SubjectTransGas Ltd/Mosquito, Grizzly Bear's Head, Lean Man I.R. #1 ** EASEMENT **
PrecisOrder a) consenting to the use by TRANSGAS LIMITED of their lawful power to acquire an easement over land within MOSQUITO, GRIZZLY BEAR'S HEAD, LEAN MAN TLE INDIAN RESERVE no. 1 in Saskatchewan, for public utility purposes and (b) in lieu of such taking, authorize the grant of the required easement.
